node.text: Had this sweet girl when I was only 25 years old💫I had no idea what an amazing blessing that would be. She was the cutest sweetest little thing!💕@antoniagorgaa I can not believe I’ve been your Mommy for 16 years! Your energy, your good heart, and your spice light up the room! You definitely give me a run for my money! I’m so happy that you’re finally 16 because according to everyone else there’s only 4 years left before you start liking me again 🤣🤣 I love you so much strong girl!! 💕💕 SWEET 16!!!! I can’t wait for your party🙌🏼💫 🎉 Happy Birthday Baby girl!!

node.text:
So many of you told me you love the new #KetoKick bars from @thatsit, that I decided to GIVEAWAY of $1,000 to AMAZON!!! 🙌🏼 We hope to help one family in a BIG WAY and to celebrate my #KetoKick being available on Amazon! ALSO 5 additional winners will get a year’s supply of @thatsit Keto Kick bars! ☕🎉

Here’s how to enter:
💙Follow me & @thatsit
💗Like and save this photo⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
💙Tag your friends (1 tag = 1 entry)⠀
💗BONUS: Drop a "☕️” on our last three posts

Giveaway open to USA only. Closes August 16th at 11:59pm PT. Winner will be contacted via DM directly from @thatsit. We will never ask you to verify winnings or for personal information outside of the app. @thatsit & @Melissagorga are the only accounts associated with this giveaway. Winners will have 48 hours to respond @thatsit to claim their prize #Thatsit

node.text: You know I’m already a big fan of @thatsit bars, so I am so excited to share their newest bar, #KetoKick! It’s an energy bar with as much caffeine as one cup of coffee ☕️💞-- talk about EXACTLY what I am going to need once the kids are back in school 💃🏻The best part is that they are just 45 calories, have no added sugar, and are certified organic. It’s the new, convenient way to get energy on the go! Get 25% off when you use code: GORGA25
